*
!README.md
!AGENTS.md
!docs/
!docs/**
!json_prompt/
!json_prompt/**
!log/
!log/**
!Veritas/
!Veritas/**
!.gitignore

# ============================================================
# 敏感文件 — 即使在白名单目录中也必须忽略
# 规则：Git 中后匹配的规则优先级更高，以下规则覆盖上方的 ! 白名单
# ============================================================

# --- 环境变量（含密钥/密码/API Key）---
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local
**/.env.production
**/.env.staging

# --- Spring Boot 敏感配置 ---
**/application-dev.yml
**/application-prod.yml
**/application-dev.properties
**/application-prod.properties

# --- 密钥与证书 ---
**/*.key
**/*.pem
**/*.p12
**/*.pfx
**/*.jks
**/*.keystore
**/*.truststore
**/secrets/
**/certs/

# --- 数据库备份与转储 ---
**/*.sql.dump
**/*.sql.gz
**/*.sql.backup
**/db-backup/

# --- 日志文件（可能含敏感运行时信息）---
**/*.log
**/logs/

# --- 操作系统生成文件 ---
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
**/desktop.ini

# --- 编辑器/IDE 临时文件（可能含本地配置）---
**/*.swp
**/*.swo
**/*~
**/.idea/
**/.vscode/
**/*.iml
